[CHECKED] Candidate family 2 is admissible only as backup. A raw concentration
statistic such as

```text
|∑_τ W_τ e^{iΘ_τ}| / ∑_τ W_τ
```

is too coarse to be the preferred object because exact conjugate pairing and
