l bottleneck is local `P_{k21}`). Earlier: **vasseur-pressure S2-E008 meta**: NEW `allow-analytic-extremizer-over-computation` (goal-design — when designing optimization-based explorations, allow explorers to find analytic extremizers instead of over-specifying SDP/LP approach; constant field extremizer made entire SDP unnecessary). Earlier: S2-E007 meta — adversarial-review-needs-complete-parallel-context, adversarial-synthesis-goal-structure update; S2-E006 meta — tool-independence-stronger-than-single-failure, quantitative-comparison-reveals-why-standard-is-standard; S2-E005 meta — bernstein-lp-poison-pill-3d, check-bypass-not-just-improve-bottleneck; S2-E002 meta — distinguish-constant-from-scaling-slack; S2-E004 meta — extract-precise-obstruction-from-failed-route, numerical-spectral-dns-diagnostic; S2-E003 meta — model-pde-comparison-for-mechanism-identification, test-improvability-before-pursuing-variations; S2-E001 meta — decomposition-audit-before-attacking-barrier, require-sensitivity-table-for-proof-analysis; E010 meta — test-generalization-before-concluding; E009 meta — adversarial-synthesis-goal-structure, adversarial-check-between-phases timing refinement; E007 meta — include-trivial-control-checks, one-task-per-exploration; E008 meta — ask-what-replaces-the-bottleneck; E006 meta — flag-cross-framework-connections.)

