laim, include at least one configuration chosen to suppress the alleged obstruction]. UPDATED: **require-mechanism-layer-maps** [exact-ns-no-near-closed-tao-circuit meta-001 — if the reduced mechanism is quadratic, represent it as a monomial hypergraph rather than just a node graph]. Prior: anatomy-of-averaged-ns-blowup-firewall meta-002 updates, anatomy-of-averaged-ns-blowup-firewall meta-001, allow-analytic-extremizer-over-computation [vasseur-pressure S2-E008], adversarial-review-needs-complete-parallel-context [S2-E007], adversarial-synthesis-goal-structure update [S2-E007], require-sensitivity-table-for-proof-analysis [S2-E001], one-task-per-exploration [E007], ask-what-replaces-the-bottleneck [E008], flag-cross-framework-connections [E006].)
 
