+
+- In the exact helical Fourier law, each ordered triad contribution to one interface-transfer ledger carries an intrinsic phase `Theta_tau`, and the preferred phase-locking observable is the exact signed-transfer versus absolute-transfer ratio `C_ell` / `D_ell` on the sign-closed triad population for a fixed smooth scale interface -> filed at `factual/navier-stokes/exact-ns-transfer-coherence-phase-observable.md` (NEW)
+- The earlier localized delayed-transfer event is now sharpened: it survives as the best physical-space event scaffold, but later phase-locking work uses it only as an event-shape anchor because the spatial cutoff breaks the clean helical triad ledger needed by the preferred phase observable -> incorporated into `factual/navier-stokes/exact-ns-physical-space-delayed-transfer-event.md` (UPDATE)
+
+### Findings extracted (meta — meta-exploration-001.md):
+
+- After a narrow Phase 0 pass leaves one preferred object pair, the next exploration should freeze that pair and test it on the smallest faithful support before reopening design -> filed at `meta/goal-design/freeze-selected-pair-before-minimal-support-audit.md` (NEW)
+- Definition-extraction is now sharpened with a transfer-ledger rule: reuse predecessor scaffolds only where they preserve the new exact ledger, and rank surviving candidates by coupling to the load-bearing ledger rather than by raw concentration summaries -> incorporated into `meta/methodology/definition-extraction-gates-computation.md` (UPDATE)
+- Explorer stall after a skeleton report plus ongoing context loading / searching -> SKIPPED as duplicate operational lesson (covered by `meta/system-behavior/explorer-stalling-and-nudge-pattern.md`)
+
+### Cross-references:
+
+- exact-ns-transfer-coherence-phase-observable.md -> exact-ns-physical-space-delayed-transfer-event.md (localized event survives as scaffold while the preferred phase-coupled pair moves to the global spectral transfer ledger)
+- freeze-selected-pair-before-minimal-support-audit.md -> fix-observability-conventions-before-precursor-search.md (broader post-selection freeze rule vs precursor-specific version)
+- freeze-selected-pair-before-minimal-support-audit.md -> check-faithful-support-shrinkage-before-narrowing.md (first decide whether the object changed at all, then freeze the surviving pair and audit minimal support)
+- definition-extraction-gates-computation.md -> coefficient-weighted-amplitude-level-leakage.md (first recover the exact ledger, then scalarize it at the amplitude/transfer level rather than by coarse packet summaries)
