- exact-ns-delayed-transfer-precursor-no-backward-memory.md -> exact-ns-physical-space-delayed-transfer-event.md (event definition survives while the preferred precursor theorem fails)
- fix-observability-conventions-before-precursor-search.md -> ask-what-replaces-the-bottleneck.md (memory audit comes before asking whether a reformulation changes the obstruction)
- fix-observability-conventions-before-precursor-search.md -> specify-failure-paths.md (when the memory audit fails, report the structural defect explicitly instead of drifting into backup-vocabulary search)

